## 7. CHANGE MANAGEMENT PROCEDURE

### Standard: Formal process for all changes to systems, code, and infrastructure

**Change Request Workflow:**
```
1. Request Phase
   ├── Create change request
   ├── Define business justification
   ├── Assess impact & risk
   └── Estimate effort & timeline

2. Approval Phase
   ├── Route to change advisory board (CAB)
   ├── CAB reviews impact & risk
   ├── CAB approves/rejects
   └── Schedule change window

3. Implementation Phase
   ├── Prepare change
   ├── Execute change
   ├── Verify success
   └── Notify stakeholders

4. Post-Implementation Phase
   ├── Monitor for issues
   ├── Document lessons learned
   ├── Update configuration management DB
   └── Archive change request

